{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1782370767622,"sessionID":"ses_102718fc5ffeKX5hudaWeJGgV5","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_K8NrcA0FMSCLQ8iv5ae3Pfph","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"D:\\workspace\\Foodike\\.agents\\skills\\cangjie-harmonyos-doc-search\\harmonyos-6.1-8k\\Guide\\dfx\\cj-hilog-guidelines\\使用HiLog打印日志\\开发示例_378e17e6.md","offset":18,"limit":40},"output":"<path>D:\\workspace\\Foodike\\.agents\\skills\\cangjie-harmonyos-doc-search\\harmonyos-6.1-8k\\Guide\\dfx\\cj-hilog-guidelines\\使用HiLog打印日志\\开发示例_378e17e6.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n18: \n19:     @Entry\n20:     @Component\n21:     class EntryView {\n22:         @State\n23:         var message: String = \"Hello World\"\n24: \n25:         func build() {\n26:             Row {\n27:                 Column {\n28:                     Button(this.message)\n29:                         .fontSize(50)\n30:                         .fontWeight(FontWeight.Bold)\n31:                         .onClick ({\n32:                             evt => this.message = \"Hello Cangjie\"\n33:                             Hilog.isLoggable(0xFF00, \"testTag\", LogLevel.Info)\n34:                             Hilog.info(0xFF00, \"testTag\", \"hello world\")\n35:                             // 设置应用日志最低打印级别，设置完成后，低于Warn级别的日志将无法打印\n36:                             Hilog.info(0x0000, 'testTag', 'this is an info level log')\n37:                             Hilog.error(0x0000, 'testTag', 'this is an error level log')\n38:                         })\n39:                 }.width(100.percent)\n40:             }.height(100.percent)\n41:         }\n42:     }\n43:    ```\n44: \n45:    以输出一条INFO级别的信息为例，表示输出一条普通信息，格式字符串为：\n46: \n47:    ```txt\n48:    hello world\n49:    ```\n50: \n51: 3. 在真机上运行该工程，单击应用/服务界面上的“Next”按钮。\n52: \n53: 4. 在DevEco Studio的底部，切换到“Log”窗口，设置日志的过滤条件。\n54: \n55:    选择当前的设备及进程，日志级别选择Verbose，搜索内容设置为“testTag”。此时窗口仅显示符合条件的日志。\n56: \n57:    打印日志结果为:\n\n(Showing lines 18-57 of 62. Use offset=58 to continue.)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"\n    @Entry\n    @Component\n    class EntryView {\n        @State\n        var message: String = \"Hello World\"\n\n        func build() {\n            Row {\n                Column {\n                    Button(this.message)\n                        .fontSize(50)\n                        .fontWeight(FontWeight.Bold)\n                        .onClick ({\n                            evt => this.message = \"Hello Cangjie\"\n                            Hilog.isLoggable(0xFF00, \"testTag\", LogLevel.Info)\n                            Hilog.info(0xFF00, \"testTag\", \"hello world\")\n                            // 设置应用日志最低打印级别，设置完成后，低于Warn级别的日志将无法打印\n                            Hilog.info(0x0000, 'testTag', 'this is an info level log')\n                            Hilog.error(0x0000, 'testTag', 'this is an error level log')","truncated":true,"loaded":[]},"title":".agents\\skills\\cangjie-harmonyos-doc-search\\harmonyos-6.1-8k\\Guide\\dfx\\cj-hilog-guidelines\\使用HiLog打印日志\\开发示例_378e17e6.md","time":{"start":1782370767614,"end":1782370767621}},"id":"prt_efd939299001Z8y2ARcnf76oK2","sessionID":"ses_102718fc5ffeKX5hudaWeJGgV5","messageID":"msg_efd92e325001CSxOWEFtaKBFSp"}}
