{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1782370800671,"sessionID":"ses_102718fc5ffeKX5hudaWeJGgV5","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_mSrfqLfNg90AuPKWw0Oh46r5","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"D:\\workspace\\Foodike\\.agents\\skills\\cangjie-harmonyos-doc-search\\harmonyos-6.1-8k\\Guide\\arkui-cj\\cj-common-components-text-input\\cj-common-components-text-input.md","offset":20,"limit":120},"output":"<path>D:\\workspace\\Foodike\\.agents\\skills\\cangjie-harmonyos-doc-search\\harmonyos-6.1-8k\\Guide\\arkui-cj\\cj-common-components-text-input\\cj-common-components-text-input.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n20: init(placeholder!: ?ResourceStr = None, text!: ?ResourceStr = None,controller!: ?TextAreaController = None)\n21: ```\n22: \n23: - 单行输入框。\n24: \n25:     ```cangjie\n26:     TextInput()\n27:     ```\n28: \n29:     ![Text](figures/Text.png)\n30: \n31: - 多行输入框。\n32: \n33:     ```cangjie\n34:     TextArea()\n35:     ```\n36: \n37:     ![Text1](figures/Text1.png)\n38: \n39: - 多行输入框文字超出一行时会自动折行。\n40: \n41:     ```cangjie\n42:     TextArea(text: \"我是TextArea我是TextArea我是TextArea我是TextArea\" ).width(300)\n43:     ```\n44: \n45:     ![Text2](figures/Text2.png)\n46: \n47: ## 自定义样式\n48: \n49: - 设置无输入时的提示文本。\n50: \n51:     ```cangjie\n52:     TextInput(placeholder: '我是提示文本')\n53:     ```\n54: \n55:     ![Text10](figures/Text10.png)\n56: \n57: - 设置输入框当前的文本内容。\n58: \n59:     ```cangjie\n60:     TextInput( placeholder: '我是提示文本', text: '我是当前文本内容' )\n61:     ```\n62: \n63:     ![Text11](figures/Text11.png)\n64: \n65: - 添加backgroundColor改变输入框的背景颜色。\n66: \n67:     ```cangjie\n68:     TextInput( placeholder: '我是提示文本', text: '我是当前文本内容' )\n69:     .backgroundColor(0x4D0A59F7)\n70:     ```\n71: \n72:     ![Text12](figures/Text12.png)\n73: \n74:     更丰富的样式可以结合[通用属性](../reference/arkui-cj/cj-universal-attributes.md)实现。\n75: \n76: ## 选中菜单\n77: \n78: 输入框中的文字被选中时会弹出包含剪切、复制、翻译的菜单。\n79: \n80: TextInput:\n81: \n82: ```cangjie\n83: TextInput( text: '这是一段文本，用来展示选中菜单')\n84: ```\n85: \n86: ![Text13](figures/Text13.png)\n87: \n88: TextArea:\n89: \n90: ```cangjie\n91: TextArea( text: '这是一段文本，用来展示选中菜单')\n92: ```\n93: \n94: ![Text13](figures/Text13.png)\n95: \n96: ## 键盘避让\n97: \n98: 键盘抬起后，具有滚动能力的容器组件在横竖屏切换时，才会生效键盘避让，若希望无滚动能力的容器组件也生效键盘避让，建议在组件外嵌套一层具有滚动能力的容器组件，比如[Scroll](../reference/arkui-cj/cj-scroll-swipe-scroll.md)、[List](../reference/arkui-cj/cj-scroll-swipe-list.md)、[Grid](../reference/arkui-cj/cj-scroll-swipe-grid.md)。\n99: \n100: <!-- run -->\n101: \n102: ```cangjie\n103: package ohos_app_cangjie_entry\n104: import kit.ArkUI.*\n105: import ohos.arkui.state_macro_manage.*\n106: \n107: @Entry\n108: @Component\n109: class EntryView {\n110:     var placeHolderArr: Array<String> = [\"1\", \"2\", \"3\", \"4\", \"5\", \"6\", \"7\"];\n111:     func build() {\n112:         Scroll() {\n113:             Column {\n114:                 ForEach(this.placeHolderArr, itemGeneratorFunc: {placeholder: String, _: Int64 =>\n115:                 TextInput( placeholder: 'TextInput ' + placeholder )\n116:                 .margin(30)}\n117:                 )\n118:             }\n119:         }\n120:         .height(100.percent)\n121:         .width(100.percent)\n122:     }\n123: }\n124: ```\n125: \n126: ![textinputkeyboardavoid](figures/TextInputKeyboardAvoid.gif)\n\n(End of file - total 126 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"init(placeholder!: ?ResourceStr = None, text!: ?ResourceStr = None,controller!: ?TextAreaController = None)\n```\n\n- 单行输入框。\n\n    ```cangjie\n    TextInput()\n    ```\n\n    ![Text](figures/Text.png)\n\n- 多行输入框。\n\n    ```cangjie\n    TextArea()\n    ```\n\n    ![Text1](figures/Text1.png)\n\n- 多行输入框文字超出一行时会自动折行。","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":".agents\\skills\\cangjie-harmonyos-doc-search\\harmonyos-6.1-8k\\Guide\\arkui-cj\\cj-common-components-text-input\\cj-common-components-text-input.md","time":{"start":1782370800663,"end":1782370800670}},"id":"prt_efd94131d001pyNSxqoAWwQ9Tb","sessionID":"ses_102718fc5ffeKX5hudaWeJGgV5","messageID":"msg_efd9395bb001yXvLnPRUHVicDg"}}
