{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1782371151938,"sessionID":"ses_102718fc5ffeKX5hudaWeJGgV5","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_FkJZn7czjJjaIuDURF6QZ8tI","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"D:\\workspace\\Foodike\\.agents\\skills\\cangjie-harmonyos-doc-search\\harmonyos-6.1-8k\\Guide\\database\\cj-data-persistence-by-preferences\\通过用户首选项实现数据持久化\\开发步骤\\开发步骤_1.md","offset":40,"limit":120},"output":"<path>D:\\workspace\\Foodike\\.agents\\skills\\cangjie-harmonyos-doc-search\\harmonyos-6.1-8k\\Guide\\database\\cj-data-persistence-by-preferences\\通过用户首选项实现数据持久化\\开发步骤\\开发步骤_1.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n40:         } \n41: \n42:         public override func onWindowStageCreate(windowStage: WindowStage): Unit {\n43:             Hilog.info(0, \"cangjie\", \"MainAbility onWindowStageCreate.\")\n44:             windowStage.loadContent(\"EntryView\")\n45: \n46:             let options = PreferencesOptions(\"myStore\")\n47:             // 获取Preferences实例\n48:             dataPreferences = Preferences.getPreferences(this.context, options)\n49:         }\n50:         // ...\n51:     }\n52:     ```\n53: \n54: 3. 写入数据。\n55: \n56:     使用put()方法保存数据到缓存的Preferences实例中。在写入数据后，如有需要，可使用flush()方法将Preferences实例的数据存储到持久化文件。\n57: \n58:     > **说明：**\n59:     >\n60:     > 当对应的键已经存在时，put()方法会覆盖其值。可以使用has()方法检查是否存在对应键值对。\n61: \n62:     示例代码如下所示：\n63: \n64:     <!-- compile -->\n65: \n66:     ```cangjie\n67:     if (dataPreferences.getOrThrow().has(\"startup\")) {\n68:         Hilog.info(0, \"cangjie\", \"The key 'startup' is contained.\")\n69:     } else {\n70:         Hilog.info(0, \"cangjie\", \"The key 'startup' does not contain.\")\n71:         // 此处以此键值对不存在时写入数据为例\n72:         dataPreferences.getOrThrow().put(\"startup\", PreferencesValueType.StringData(\"auto\"))\n73:     }\n74:     ```\n75: \n76: 4. 读取数据。\n77: \n78:     使用get()方法获取数据，即指定键对应的值。如果值为null或者非默认值类型，则返回默认数据。\n79: \n80:     示例代码如下所示：\n81: \n82:     <!-- compile -->\n83: \n84:     ```cangjie\n85:     // xxx.cj\n86:     let val = dataPreferences.getOrThrow().get(\"startup\", PreferencesValueType.StringData(\"default\"))\n87:     match(val) {\n88:         case PreferencesValueType.StringData(n) => Hilog.info(0, \"cangjie\", \"The startup's value\")\n89:         case _ => Hilog.info(0, \"cangjie\", \"error, value not string\")\n90:     }\n91:     ```\n92: \n93: 5. 删除数据。\n94: \n95:     使用delete()方法删除指定键值对，示例代码如下所示：\n96: \n97:     <!-- compile -->\n98: \n99:     ```cangjie\n100:     // xxx.cj\n101:     dataPreferences.getOrThrow().delete(\"startup\")\n102:     ```\n103: \n104: 6. 数据持久化。\n105: \n106:     应用存入数据到Preferences实例后，可以使用flush()方法实现数据持久化。示例代码如下所示：\n107: \n108:     <!-- compile -->\n109: \n110:     ```cangjie\n111:     // xxx.cj\n112:     dataPreferences.getOrThrow().flush()\n113:     ```\n114: \n115: 7. 订阅数据变更。\n116: \n117:     应用订阅数据变更需要自定义Callback作为回调方法。订阅的Key值发生变更后，当执行flush()方法时，Callback被触发回调。示例代码如下所示：\n118: \n119:     为实现订阅数据变更功能，需要定义如下类：\n120: \n121:     <!-- compile -->\n122: \n123:     ```cangjie\n124:     // xxx.cj\n125:     // 自定义回调函数\n126:     class Callback <: Callback1Argument<String> {\n127:         public func invoke(err: ?BusinessException, arg: String): Unit {\n128:             Hilog.info(1, \"info\", \"callback： ${arg.toString()}\")\n129:         }\n130:     }\n131:     ```\n132: \n133:     实现订阅数据变更功能的核心代码是：\n134: \n135:     <!-- compile -->\n136: \n137:     ```cangjie\n138:     let preferenceCallback = Callback()\n139:     dataPreferences.getOrThrow().on(PreferencesEvent.PreferencesChange, preferenceCallback)\n140:     // 数据产生变更，由“auto”变为“manual”\n141:     dataPreferences.getOrThrow().put(\"startup\", PreferencesValueType.StringData(\"manual\"))\n142:     Hilog.info(0, \"cangjie\", \"Succeeded in putting the value of 'startup'.\")\n143:     dataPreferences.getOrThrow().flush()\n144:     ```\n145: \n146: 8. 删除指定文件。\n\n(End of file - total 146 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"        } \n\n        public override func onWindowStageCreate(windowStage: WindowStage): Unit {\n            Hilog.info(0, \"cangjie\", \"MainAbility onWindowStageCreate.\")\n            windowStage.loadContent(\"EntryView\")\n\n            let options = PreferencesOptions(\"myStore\")\n            // 获取Preferences实例\n            dataPreferences = Preferences.getPreferences(this.context, options)\n        }\n        // ...\n    }\n    ```\n\n3. 写入数据。\n\n    使用put()方法保存数据到缓存的Preferences实例中。在写入数据后，如有需要，可使用flush()方法将Preferences实例的数据存储到持久化文件。\n\n    > **说明：**\n    >","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":".agents\\skills\\cangjie-harmonyos-doc-search\\harmonyos-6.1-8k\\Guide\\database\\cj-data-persistence-by-preferences\\通过用户首选项实现数据持久化\\开发步骤\\开发步骤_1.md","time":{"start":1782371151907,"end":1782371151937}},"id":"prt_efd996fbf001wI9znZ3JD8ELXc","sessionID":"ses_102718fc5ffeKX5hudaWeJGgV5","messageID":"msg_efd98643100195RjStvqy6PhKr"}}
