{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1782372068425,"sessionID":"ses_102718fc5ffeKX5hudaWeJGgV5","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_S8pPz6zMRgTvUl7kFAt8ayLt","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"D:\\workspace\\Foodike\\.agents\\skills\\cangjie-harmonyos-doc-search\\harmonyos-6.1-8k\\Guide\\arkui-cj\\rendering_control\\cj-rendering-control-ifelse\\ifelse条件渲染\\使用场景\\使用if进行条件渲染_903772d5.md","offset":1,"limit":80},"output":"<path>D:\\workspace\\Foodike\\.agents\\skills\\cangjie-harmonyos-doc-search\\harmonyos-6.1-8k\\Guide\\arkui-cj\\rendering_control\\cj-rendering-control-ifelse\\ifelse条件渲染\\使用场景\\使用if进行条件渲染_903772d5.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: ### 使用if进行条件渲染\n2: \n3: <!-- run -->\n4: \n5: ```cangjie\n6: package ohos_app_cangjie_entry\n7: import kit.ArkUI.*\n8: import ohos.arkui.state_macro_manage.*\n9: \n10: @Entry\n11: @Component\n12: class EntryView {\n13:   @State var count: Int64 = 0;\n14:   func build() {\n15:     Column() {\n16:       Text(\"count=${this.count}\")\n17: \n18:       if (this.count > 0) {\n19:         Text(\"count is positive\")\n20:           .fontColor(Color.Green)\n21:       }\n22: \n23:       Button('increase count')\n24:         .onClick({ e =>\n25:           this.count++;\n26:         })\n27: \n28:       Button('decrease count')\n29:         .onClick({ e =>\n30:           this.count--;\n31:         })\n32:     }\n33:   }\n34: }\n35: ```\n36: \n37: if语句的每个分支都包含一个构建函数。此类构建函数必须创建一个或多个子组件。在初始渲染时，if语句会执行构建函数，并将生成的子组件添加到其父组件中。\n38: \n39: 每当if或else if条件语句中使用的状态变量发生变化时，条件语句都会更新并重新评估新的条件值。如果条件值评估发生了变化，这意味着需要构建另一个条件分支。此时ArkUI框架将：\n40: \n41: 1.删除所有以前渲染的（早期分支的）组件。\n42: \n43: 2.执行新分支的构造函数，将生成的子组件添加到其父组件中。\n44: \n45: 在以上示例中，如果count从0增加到1，那么if语句更新，条件count > 0将重新评估，评估结果将从false更改为true。因此，将执行条件为真分支的构造函数，创建一个Text组件，并将它添加到父组件Column中。如果后续count更改为0，则Text组件将从Column组件中删除。由于没有else分支，因此不会执行新的构造函数。\n\n(End of file - total 45 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"### 使用if进行条件渲染\n\n<!-- run -->\n\n```cangjie\npackage ohos_app_cangjie_entry\nimport kit.ArkUI.*\nimport ohos.arkui.state_macro_manage.*\n\n@Entry\n@Component\nclass EntryView {\n  @State var count: Int64 = 0;\n  func build() {\n    Column() {\n      Text(\"count=${this.count}\")\n\n      if (this.count > 0) {\n        Text(\"count is positive\")\n          .fontColor(Color.Green)","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":".agents\\skills\\cangjie-harmonyos-doc-search\\harmonyos-6.1-8k\\Guide\\arkui-cj\\rendering_control\\cj-rendering-control-ifelse\\ifelse条件渲染\\使用场景\\使用if进行条件渲染_903772d5.md","time":{"start":1782372068416,"end":1782372068425}},"id":"prt_efda76b89001SPnfW3VRPWCFtF","sessionID":"ses_102718fc5ffeKX5hudaWeJGgV5","messageID":"msg_efda6f7b2001eizfWpTi2kxQ06"}}
